short_description: PREMIUM QUALITY: EOW XPEDITE PRO telescopic casting and spinning fishing rods are crafted from 24T carbon and epoxy for sensitivity, durability, and performance. The length of the tip, 2nd and 3rd sections are specially designed to give you the best casting feel just like a 1pc traditional rod.

VERSATILE & LIGHTWEIGHT: This fishing rod works great for trout fishing, bass fishing, kayak fishing, and more. The lightweight rod feels balanced in your hand, improves your range of motion, and reduces fatigue to a minimum. The closed length is less than 17”, so you can take this travel fishing rod anywhere and enjoy fishing on your vacation or trip!

EASY & FAST ASSEMBLE: Just extend each section starting from the tip until it stops. After fishing, simply collapse the rods by starting from the bottom with a twist, and you can leave the reel/line/hooks/lure on the fishing pole. You can keep the sets in your car or backpack, so next time, it’s very quick and easy to get ready to fish.

QUALITY CONTROL & PROFESSIONAL SERVICE: EOW is ISO9000 compliant with strict quality control throughout production. Each rod undergoes a deadweight test to ensure top quality before shipment. As a professional fishing gear manufacturer, EOW provides top-notch after-sales service. If you have any questions about our products, our team will provide satisfactory solutions within 12 hours.
